  Developer ID (notarized) build: NOT sandboxed, so the global hotkeys
  (Input Monitoring) and the screen-saver install (~/Library/Screen Savers)
  work. Hardened runtime is enabled via build settings for notarization; no
  special entitlements are required for non-sandboxed global event monitoring.
  The Mac App Store build uses MacWallpaper-MAS.entitlements instead.
-->
